## Rule 0: Tool Requirements & Setup

### 0.1 Required Tools

| Tool | Purpose | Installation |
|------|---------|-------------|
| **Pencil MCP** | Wireframe & prototype design | Cursor Extensions Marketplace |
| **Codex CLI** | AI-assisted code generation | `npm install -g @openai/codex` |
| **QwenCLI** | Main code implementation | Built-in (Qwen Code) |
| **GitHub CLI (`gh`)** | PR creation, issue management | `winget install GitHub.cli` |
| **Telegram Bot** | Thread notifications | `scripts/send-dev-report.js`, `scripts/send-changelog.js` |
| **Node.js** | Script execution | `winget install OpenJS.NodeJS` |

### 0.2 Pencil MCP Setup

**Pencil MCP là Cursor extension** — cài qua Cursor Extensions Marketplace.

**Sử dụng:**
- Command Palette → `Pencil: Create New Design`
- Tên design: `<feature-name>-<ticket-id>`
- Export: PNG/SVG → `Docs/01-product/wireframes/<feature>/`
- Save: `Docs/01-product/wireframes/<feature>/<design>.pencil`

**Design System Library (Reuse):**
1. Feature đầu tiên → tạo component library → `Docs/01-product/design-system/<project>-library.pencil`
2. Các feature sau → `Pencil: Import Components from Library` → reuse → chỉ tạo mới components chưa có

### 0.3 Gemini CLI Setup (Gemini 3.1 Pro for Visual)

```bash
npm install -g @google/generative-ai-cli
export GEMINI_API_KEY="your-key"  # https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
```

**When to use:** Color palette refinement, visual hierarchy, icon generation (SVG output), layout optimization.

### 0.4 Telegram Bot Setup

```bash
# Bot credentials in .env.local (NEVER commit)
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN="your-bot-token"
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID="your-chat-id"

# Test notification
node scripts/send-dev-report.js "Test message" --thread 727
```

### 0.5 GitHub CLI Setup

```bash
gh auth login
gh repo set-default PersonalProjectJob/Job360
gh auth status
```

