## Rule 7: Subagent Communication Flow

### 7.1 Feature Branch (Full Workflow)

```
Phase 0: Plan Mode (feature/* only)
  → Create Master Doc → Product, Engineering, QA, Tasks docs
  → Master Doc phân chia docs cho từng role
  → User approves Master Doc ✅
  ↓
Phase 1: Product-Designer (Thread 727)
  → Design System Audit → Wireframes via Pencil MCP
  → Update Product Doc with Pencil link + Audit results
  → Report Thread 727
  ↓ [User reviews & approves design]
  ↓
Phase 2: Frontend-Developer & Backend-Developer (Thread 727, parallel)
  → Read Engineering Doc + Design artifacts
  → Implement → PR → test branch
  → Report Thread 727
  ↓ [Both complete & PRs → test]
  ↓
Phase 3: QA-Tester (Thread 735)
  → Run tests → Report Thread 735
  → If QA PASS → Report Thread 718 → Merge
  → If QA FAIL → Report user → Wait for decision
```

### 7.2 Blocking Conditions

| Subagent | Blocked By | Unblock Condition |
|----------|-----------|-------------------|
| Product-Designer | Master Doc not approved | User approves |
| Frontend-Developer | Design not approved | User approves design |
| Backend-Developer | Design not approved | User approves design |
| QA-Tester | FE + BE PRs not on test | Both PRs merged to test |

