### Report Checklist
Every subagent report must have:
- [ ] Agent name & feature
- [ ] Status (completed/blocked/failed)
- [ ] Artifacts created/modified
- [ ] Next steps
- [ ] Timestamp (date + time)
- [ ] Links to relevant docs/PRs
- [ ] Correct thread
